{"tid":940561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"訓咗幾個月，想問今個星期日係咪會打10號風球","createTime":"2018-12-14T04:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T13:20:05.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0edcc3410c386104d4172c25d9da2a5262ac47","tid":940561,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"按照現時山竹的移動路徑，下周日(16日)天氣會明顯轉壞，發出8號信號的機會是相當高，至於會否發出9號或10號信號，要視乎山竹明日的移動路徑會否受影響，現不會排除任何可能。 <br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇新聞，見到有個超強颱風叫山竹，會今個星期日即係16號打正香港，想問今個星期日係咪會掛10號風球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400f36b4ad372526433e0b4e9c09c705fb305239","tid":940561,"uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefa6956d6b637c38fa771bac70ec77cccd521a1","tid":940561,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"放心，樓主唔會打風<br />\n你可以繼續瞓返覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae0ddc500efbe1aaf6655c343bd4200ecd5a885","tid":940561,"uid":176802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪以為自己好幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見咁少人睬你 我嚟應下你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541945bbec6026a890cc8989ebde16c1c0fe52ec","tid":940561,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"係，記得星期六晚係公司紮定營先"},{"pid":"2fe3c2acff70680ea80fe4c2358fe133b25f4378","tid":940561,"uid":143348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n第2日地鐵瀨屎 仲有個鬼佬比人影"},{"pid":"fd112dea682181d0fa4e10ac2ac5b018b4066c7a","tid":940561,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2fe3c2acff70680ea80fe4c2358fe133b25f4378","tid":940561,"uid":143348,"like":0,"dislike":0